actions.text: Measure failed of passage in House under suspension of the rules, roll call #690 (252-135).

official_title: A resolution providing for consideration of conference reports on the same day reported, and for other purposes.

summary.text: Provides for consideration of conference reports on the same day reported in the House of Representatives for the remainder of the second session of the Ninety-third Congress.
